title: SB Chronicles Unplugged: Justin Brock presents Grant Taylor
description:
In preparation for our upcoming SB Chronicles Vol. 2 release, Nike SB pro Justin Brock introduces a special "unplugged" version of SOTY Grant Taylor's part from SB Chronicles Vol. 1.

Nike SB's new full-length video The SB Chronicles Vol. 2 hits iTunes on December 10th.
